str.count(sub[, start[, end]]) ‚Üí Count occurrences of substring.
str.find(sub[, start[, end]]) ‚Üí Index of first occurrence, -1 if not found.
str.rfind(sub[, start[, end]]) ‚Üí Index of last occurrence, -1 if not found.
str.index(sub[, start[, end]]) ‚Üí Like find(), but raises ValueError if not found.
str.rindex(sub[, start[, end]]) ‚Üí Like rfind(), but raises ValueError if not found.
str.startswith(prefix[, start[, end]]) ‚Üí Checks if string starts with prefix.
str.endswith(suffix[, start[, end]]) ‚Üí Checks if string ends with suffix.
str.partition(sep) ‚Üí Splits into tuple (before, sep, after) at first occurrence.
str.rpartition(sep) ‚Üí Splits at last occurrence.
str.split(sep=None, maxsplit=-1) ‚Üí Splits string into list.
str.rsplit(sep=None, maxsplit=-1) ‚Üí Splits string from right.
str.splitlines(keepends=False) ‚Üí Splits string at line breaks.
str.replace(old, new[, count]) ‚Üí Replaces occurrences of a substring.
Trimming/Stripping
str.strip([chars]) ‚Üí Removes leading/trailing whitespace or characters.
str.lstrip([chars]) ‚Üí Removes leading characters.
str.rstrip([chars]) ‚Üí Removes trailing characters.
str.removeprefix(prefix) ‚Üí Removes prefix if present (Python 3.9+).
str.removesuffix(suffix) ‚Üí Removes suffix if present (Python 3.9+).
Joining/Formatting
str.join(iterable) ‚Üí Joins elements of iterable with the string as separator.
str.format(*args, **kwargs) ‚Üí Formats string with placeholders.
str.format_map(mapping) ‚Üí Like format(), but uses a mapping (dict).
str.maketrans(x, y=None, z='') ‚Üí Returns translation table for translate().
str.translate(table) ‚Üí Translates string using a translation table.
Padding/Aligning
str.center(width[, fillchar]) ‚Üí Centers string.
str.ljust(width[, fillchar]) ‚Üí Left-aligns string.
str.rjust(width[, fillchar]) ‚Üí Right-aligns string.
str.zfill(width) ‚Üí Pads string with zeros on the left.
Encoding/Decoding
str.encode(encoding='utf-8', errors='strict') ‚Üí Encodes string to bytes.
str.decode() ‚Üí Only on bytes, not string.
Other Useful Methods
str.isnumeric() ‚Üí Checks if all chars are numeric.
str.isprintable() ‚Üí Checks if all chars are printable.
str.expandtabs(tabsize=8) ‚Üí Replaces tabs \t with spaces.


